{"entity":{"id":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","type":"chapter","slug":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","label":"Ps.81","rawId":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","book":{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","slug":"ps","label":"Psalms","subtitle":"Poetry-Wisdom","count":2461,"description":"150 chapters, 1026 people, 118 places"}},"stats":{"verses":16,"people":3,"places":2,"events":0},"nodes":[{"id":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Ps.81","slug":"ps_81","score":16},{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Psalms","slug":"ps","score":2461},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":4},{"id":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Jacob (Israel)","slug":"israel_682","score":2},{"id":"rechuDYJoK32gmrME","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Joseph (son of Jacob)","slug":"joseph_1710","score":1},{"id":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Egypt","slug":"egypt_362","score":2},{"id":"rec1irrySVGkYieCr","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Meribah (of Kadesh)","slug":"meribah_782","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","target":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","label":"part of"},{"source":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","target":"rechuDYJoK32gmrME","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reckzN0BCHJ2e6t81","target":"rec1irrySVGkYieCr","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recKv7Qw49TgjwQPy","ref":"Ps.81.1","text":"Sing aloud unto God our strength: make a joyful noise unto the God of Jacob."},{"id":"recdl2QVKMG25tBec","ref":"Ps.81.2","text":"Take a psalm, and bring hither the timbrel, the pleasant harp with the psaltery."},{"id":"recFbAdqcz0fUzuJV","ref":"Ps.81.3","text":"Blow up the trumpet in the new moon, in the time appointed, on our solemn feast day."},{"id":"recQG0Sa01O27cCAB","ref":"Ps.81.4","text":"For this was a statute for Israel, and a law of the God of Jacob."},{"id":"recNolSJtCDUGkwi7","ref":"Ps.81.5","text":"This he ordained in Joseph for a testimony, when he went out through the land of Egypt: where I heard a language that I understood not."},{"id":"recayxLjkb4Y6mIRa","ref":"Ps.81.6","text":"I removed his shoulder from the burden: his hands were delivered from the pots."},{"id":"recQUSN56u6A0ZZH2","ref":"Ps.81.7","text":"Thou calledst in trouble, and I delivered thee; I answered thee in the secret place of thunder: I proved thee at the waters of Meribah. Selah."},{"id":"recNLQtWyyOpqxhmF","ref":"Ps.81.8","text":"Hear, O my people, and I will testify unto thee: O Israel, if thou wilt hearken unto me;"}]}
